 Literature in Contemporary Society." Hans Eichner presents a "Defence of Literature" and discusses the role of a Faculty of Humanities. Finally, Malcolm F. McGregor speaks to the questions, "What are the humanities?" and "What is an education in the humanities."  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aEducation. 7aEDUCATION / Philosophy, Theory & Social Aspects.2bisacsh1 aBlais, Marie-Claire, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCoward, Harold C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCoward, Harold, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aDavies, Robertson, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEichner, Hans, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrant, George, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMcgregor, Malcolm F., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPriestley, F. E. L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVlastos, Gregory, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWoods, John, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWoods, John, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010z978311127416408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010z978311127724040uhttps://doi.org/10.51644/978088920549940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780889205499423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780889205499/original  a978-3-11-127416-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010b2010  a978-3-11-127724-0  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010b2010  aGBV-deGruyter-alles